{"tid":366167,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［轉載］［唔知真假］支國一線部隊一年最多開40槍，一百部坦克行百米壞80部","createTime":"2017-08-19T19:37:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-20T01:23:23.000Z","uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"88b5d22a72cfb471ab4a795cf9a76fec61337799","tid":366167,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T19:37:55.000Z","msg":"[轉發]<br />\n昨天跟朋友吃飯聊天......這個朋友是副連退下來的，當了十幾年兵。<br />\n<br />\n聊到中印對峙的問題，跟我說：軍隊已經爛到根了！沒有戰鬥力！他在部隊問軍人如果打仗了怎麼辦？<br />\n<br />\n所有的軍人都回答：我首先在後面幹掉旅長！再幹掉上面的領導！<br />\n<br />\n看來？受壓迫的不只是我們老百姓而已！那些基層的軍人受壓迫的更狠！<br />\n<br />\n朋友的部隊是一線作戰部隊，已經腐敗到什麼程度了？跟我說了兩點震驚了我！<br />\n<br />\n第一、一百輛坦克出去拉練跑了一百米，壞了八十多輛！原因是所有的保養費、維修費、包括燃油錢全被貪了！想著也不會打仗，不貪白不貪！<br />\n<br />\n第二、每個士兵一年訓練的子彈是四十發，但是他們只能用五發，其餘35發子彈貪了！怎麼貪呢？每年大學生軍訓，明碼實價，你如果想打真槍實彈？五塊錢一發！<br />\n<br />\n一線作戰部隊如此，就更不談二線部隊和預備役了！<br />\n<br />\n[熊大評]：難怪共軍遭遇印軍......雙方必須用石頭互砸！多留幾顆子彈，回家可以賣個好價錢啊！"},{"pid":"8fe3435ce24d7986a7c556a08119b344b210d31a","tid":366167,"uid":19287,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T00:04:36.000Z","msg":"每個士兵一年訓練的子彈是四十發<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n會唔會吹大左"},{"pid":"02ee6956408df0bdb9457d19716f7bf7129b893c","tid":366167,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T00:17:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>每個士兵一年訓練的子彈是四十發<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n會唔會吹大左</blockquote><br />\n有乜出奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b385ce8fa6b1e4cc4999e6cb508863ab789505e","tid":366167,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T00:19:45.000Z","msg":"高估敵人好過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abb53052b7cfafff6eb4dc484491054f11ccaaf2","tid":366167,"uid":2445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T00:20:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>每個士兵一年訓練的子彈是四十發<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n會唔會吹大左</blockquote><br />\n有乜出奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n分分鐘警犬ptu都唔止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1f410ba6179849df7bc79fbf55410ca3b373663","tid":366167,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T00:29:18.000Z","msg":"吹大左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87d34dbf10ed82ce1d3e04f19b5e65b034618b2e","tid":366167,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T00:34:25.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"7665523c4c530874285336c6fb79dcf074049a2e","tid":366167,"uid":68094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T00:49:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"24f025510adefc8fd8f17714ff37d27c8208da94","tid":366167,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T00:56:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有軍訓，9成係駐紮沿海城市 ／內陸大城市的部隊<br />\n<br />\n垃圾係正常<br />\n<br />\n西藏，新疆 青海個邊唔信咁垃圾，</blockquote><br />\n嗰邊測試武器多，士兵生血癌機率都高好多"},{"pid":"e4a5fa60e424cdf783e7399c0aea7b8a8d85c1f8","tid":366167,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T01:02:10.000Z","msg":"老老豆豆，唔信<br />\n邊防部隊，尤其係新疆嗰堆<br />\n殺維吾爾族無數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a519315c3131e0f769552ba8ee445babdd194ba","tid":366167,"uid":42764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T01:23:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>每個士兵一年訓練的子彈是四十發<br />\n會唔會吹大左</blockquote><br />\n有乜出奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n之前好似有cs練槍法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}